name: Tetris+
overview: Tetris+ is clone of the popular puzzle game Tetris or the Commodore VIC-20 (using a 3K expansion). It was developed BY NBLA000 and NIPPUR72 and published by VICtalian Software in 2008. NBLA000 alcos coded an earlier Tetris game for the VIC called Tetris Deluxe, which was an enhanced version of a game that came before it written by another coder.
